poem:
I have never been in love 
Is it that easy? 
To be "in" love ?
Nope , 
It's the most miserably beautiful thing ;
A human is capable of .....
Miserably beautiful ;
Happily painful;
Peacefully chaotic ;
Securely scared ;
Hateful yet lovable ;
ALL THIS THINGS 
AT THE SAME TIME 
I BET 
ITS DIFFICULT YET SIMPLE
TO LOVE...

I don't know 
If m the only one 
To feel this way; 
I just fear ; 
Fear that you might hesitate; 
Hesitate to stay!
You would think twice ,
Abt the times we spent 
Making memories that might later make your eyes teary!
What we share; 
How we are;
What does it costs?
Is it something so worthy ;
That we can't tell if it's worthless?
I just know 
You and me 
Are meant forever to be!
So , just calm down baby;
I don't know about the good times 
But I promise in your bad times you will see me by your side standing steady ! 
I love you!

I have never been in love 
Is it that easy? 
To be "in" love ?
Nope , 
It's the most miserably beautiful thing ;
A human is capable of .....
Miserably beautiful ;
Happily painful;
Peacefully chaotic ;
Securely scared ;
Hateful yet lovable ;
ALL THIS THINGS 
AT THE SAME TIME 
I BET 
ITS DIFFICULT YET SIMPLE
TO LOVE...
